{"tid":2321493,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭生多謝連登仔！！","createTime":"2020-12-11T13:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T23:40:08.000Z","uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1589a33a4029da248f329c3c51f4e83638c6e10a","tid":2321493,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"【2020 外賣聖誕套餐】<br />\n<br />\n🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨<br />\n💬💬💬收到好多查詢💬💬<br />\n🎄聖誕2、4、6人餐 今日開始可以訂喇！😉即日拎都得㗎～<br />\n由於反應熱烈 👨🏻&zwj;🍳製作需時，客人請預先☎️致電店舖查詢 及預訂<br />\n<br />\n🚐🚚🚐🚚🚐🚚🚐🚚🚐🚚🚐🚚🚐🚚🚐🚚<br />\n都收到好多客人問💬  送唔送貨🛵<br />\n送呀！送呀！送呀！你肯俾💰 我肯送！🛵 Call車可以到既地方都送！<br />\n客人同 附近分店 ☑️確認訂單及💰轉帳後，由店舖為客人代為call車🚚<br />\n🚚💰車費需由客人到付。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️⚠️注意：☑️確認訂單及💰轉帳後，不設退款。<br />\n⚠️⚠️注意：實際車費及路面情況，可能因為當時的時間有所出入。<br />\n<br />\n🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n另外 多謝咁多位網友👩🏻&zwj;💻👨🏻&zwj;💻  同 💡 <span class=\"xx-large\">連登大神</span>幫推🥺<br />\n🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n唔知燒山有冇acc呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3e04ec370c38a50e61af07a35a3f60050f0ec0","tid":2321493,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"識用燈泡個圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好cute"},{"pid":"f3fc12b41cf7d899aa3172570f7abb6452c7d4cd","tid":2321493,"uid":30503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"唔該晒"},{"pid":"9ce281d1c5372ffacacc3d11ceda9306cbaaf63f","tid":2321493,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:03:13.000Z","msg":"如果佢應承收一個禮拜聲唔好燈侵侵，我即刻幫襯<img src=\"/asset